<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.170742>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Parapanteles rooibos n. sp. wing venation (A), male genitalia (B), metasoma lateral view (C), mesosoma dorsal view (D), female genitalia (E), propodeum dorsal view (F), metasomal tergites dorsal view (G) and mesosoma lateral view (H)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/170742/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.170743>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Parapanteles rooibos n. sp. cocoon close up (A) and among needles of host plant (B), rooibos plantation (C) and host Isturgia exerraria (Prout) caterpillar on rooibos plant (D). Photo A by Alejandro Valerio; B from field collection by Dr. Justin Hatting (ARC­SGI, South Africa); C & D copyright ENTOCARE and used with permission." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/170743/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

